'''Micro miniature''' (also called '''micro art''' or '''micro sculpture''') is a [[fine art]] form. Micro [[figurine|miniatures]] are made by [[microscope]]. It originated at the end of 20th century.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dissercat.com/content/khudozhestvennaya-mikrominiatyura-kak-sredstvo-postroeniya-mikrokosma-kultury|title=Определение из диссертации Станислава Коненко "Художественная микроминиатюра как средство построения микрокосма культуры"}}</ref>
